'''唐浩嘉'''（{{lang-en|'''Kiko Tong'''}}），前名'''唐曉彤'''<ref>{{cite news |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200819/bkn-20200819183919770-0819_00862_001.html |title=唐浩嘉為圓歌手夢　辭工唔再做護士 |quote=歌手唐浩嘉（Kiko，前名唐曉彤）原是全職護士…… |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2020-08-19 |accessdate=2022-06-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[香港|香港]][[流行音乐|流行音樂]]女[[歌手|歌手]]，作品有《一刻女生》，《情人傳心術》，《花非花》

==簡介==
===經歷===
唐浩嘉出生於[[香港|香港]]，是家中最小的女兒，家裡還有哥哥和姐姐<ref name="影后">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171103/bkn-20171103044559335-1103_00862_001.html |title=表演欲超強！唐曉彤細細個就做影后 |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-11-03 |accessdate=2017-11-03 |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701204243/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171103/bkn-20171103044559335-1103_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她出道前是[[護士|護士]]<ref name="酒吧">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171205/bkn-20171205011506021-1205_00862_001.html |title=「白衣天使」顧形象！唐曉彤自爆蒲得少 |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-12-05 |accessdate=2017-12-05 |archive-date=2020-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702194802/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171205/bkn-20171205011506021-1205_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{fact|2011年，她參加“[[Neway|Neway]]×新城娛樂台big girls battle”歌唱比賽獲得冠軍，獲得機會接受聲樂、演戲、跳舞及[[貓步|貓步]]訓練。}}

{{fact|2016至2017年，她亦有參與大專及中學校園巡唱, 並演唱個人創作作品《Stand Up Again》和《Leave Me Alone》等等。}}

2016年底，她加入明星籃球隊“Venus”參與慈善友誼賽<ref name="重新出發">{{cite news|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170907/bkn-20170907044538368-0907_00862_001.html|title=之前滿約要做番護士　唐曉彤重新出發！|author=|website=香港[[東網|東網]]|language=zh-hk|date=2017-09-07|accessdate=2017-10-27|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701105804/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170907/bkn-20170907044538368-0907_00862_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{when|現時參與拍攝、演出及音樂製作}}。

唐浩嘉也因擁有一雙長腿<ref name="失聲">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171108/bkn-20171108044559972-1108_00862_001.html |title=演出前失聲　唐曉彤要食藥打針先頂得住 |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-11-08 |accessdate=2017-11-08 |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701111029/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171108/bkn-20171108044559972-1108_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="操拳">{{Cite web|title=唐曉彤操拳練意志 想同太極合作玩音樂|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170913/bkn-20170913034544468-0913_00862_001.html|accessdate=2017-09-13|work=香港東網|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703191818/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170913/bkn-20170913034544468-0913_00862_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而被贊“長腿女神”<ref name="聖誕女郎">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171226/bkn-20171226034528993-1226_00862_001.html |title=見到都暖笠笠！唐曉彤化身聖誕女郎曬Body |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-12-26 |accessdate=2017-12-26 |archive-date=2020-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702170339/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171226/bkn-20171226034528993-1226_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===個人生活===
唐浩嘉熱愛運動<ref name="正能量">{{Cite web|title=正能量爆燈！唐曉彤為慈善送歌打氣|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170921/bkn-20170921063028715-0921_00862_001.html|accessdate=2020-07-18|work=香港東網|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702211240/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170921/bkn-20170921063028715-0921_00862_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，平時喜愛[[長跑|長跑]]和[[登山|登山]]<ref name="合照">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/bkn-20171113051522422-1113_00862_001.html |title=巧遇單車男神　唐曉彤把握機會求合照 |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-11-13 |accessdate=2017-11-13 |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701171708/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/bkn-20171113051522422-1113_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，還參加過[[馬拉松|馬拉松]]<ref name="罕有">{{cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171203/bkn-20171203054538583-1203_00862_001.html |title=罕有性感！唐曉彤曬43吋長腿行善好吸睛 |author= |website=香港東網 |language=zh-hk |date=2017-12-03 |accessdate=2017-12-04 |archive-date=2020-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703153204/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171203/bkn-20171203054538583-1203_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="合照" />。她曾與明星籃球隊“Venus”成員一起學[[泰拳|泰拳]]<ref name="操拳" />。

為了穿旗袍好看，她曾特意進行長跑訓練和節食。她在出道以後也開始努力學習和提升普通話水準。

